command: for f in tmp/3_big_serie_CT/* ; do dcmdump +L all -M $f ; done
for f in tmp/3_big_serie_CT/* ; do dcmdump +L +P PatientName +P PatientID +P Modality $f; done
for f in tmp/3_big_serie_CT/* ; do dcmdump +L +P PatientName +P PatientID +P StudyDate $f; done
for f in tmp/3_big_serie_CT/* ; do dcm2json $f dcmtk_json_csv/$(basename $f).json ; done
find tmp/3_big_serie_CT -type f -name "*.dcm" | parallel dcmdump +L all -M {}
